OL,3,CUnderground strike set to shut key
OL,4,Clines as drivers walkout in row over
OL,5,Crosters
OL,7,FKey Tube lines in central London are
OL,8,Fset to shut next week because of a
OL,9,Fstrike by Underground drivers.
OL,11,FTransport for London warned commuters
OL,12,Fto expect four days of 'significant
OL,13,Fdisruption' during the walkout by RMT
OL,14,Fmembers.
OL,16,FThe Piccadilly and Circle Lines are
OL,17,Flikely to be at a standstill from
OL,18,FTuesday afternoon along with busy
OL,19,Fsections of the Central and
OL,20,FMetropolitan Lines.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/5
