PN,40902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1776514266
OL,3,CUnderground strike set to shut key
OL,4,Clines as drivers walkout in row over
OL,5,Crosters
OL,7,FNo trains will run between Aldgate and
OL,8,FBaker Street on the Metropolitan Line
OL,9,Fand between Liverpool Street and White
OL,10,FCity on the Central Line.
OL,12,FPassengers travelling to the City and
OL,13,FWest End are expected to switch to the
OL,14,FElizabeth Line, putting increased
OL,15,Fpressure on one of the capital's
OL,16,Falready busy routes.
OL,18,FServices are unlikely to return to
OL,19,Fnormal until Friday afternoon.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/5
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
