FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1776514266
OL,3,CUnderground strike set to shut key
OL,4,Clines as drivers walkout in row over
OL,5,Crosters
OL,7,FThe strike was called by RMT leaders
OL,8,Fin protest at plans to change drivers'
OL,9,Frosters from a five-day week to four
OL,10,Fdays and to 34 hours instead of 35.
OL,12,FThe union has indicated it wants at 32-
OL,13,Fhour week.
OL,15,FClaire Mann, TfL's Chief Operating
OL,16,FOfficer, said: "The changes would be
OL,17,Fvoluntary, there would be no reduction
OL,18,Fin contractual hours and those who
OL,19,Fwish to continue a five-day working
OL,20,Fweek pattern would be able to do so."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/5
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1776514266
OL,3,CUnderground strike set to shut key
OL,4,Clines as drivers walkout in row over
OL,5,Crosters
OL,7,FShe added: "We urge the RMT to call
OL,8,Foff this action, which will disrupt
OL,9,FLondoners, and continue to engage with
OL,10,Fus.
OL,12,F"If this strike action goes ahead
OL,13,Fcustomers should check before they
OL,14,Ftravel as on some days during the
OL,15,Fstrike, there will be significant
OL,16,Fdisruption and the level of service we
OL,17,Fcan provide will vary across lines."
OL,19,FA proposed voluntary 'pilot' roster on
OL,20,Fthe Bakerloo Line has been agreed by
OL,21,Fthe other main union, Aslef.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/5
